Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:21.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,∮ Just a come-on from those gals on Seventh Avenue. ∮\N{\rCHT}只有第七大道的妓女們對我有興趣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.92,0:01:30.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,∮ So lonesome that I took some comfort there. ∮\N{\rCHT}寂寞難耐的時候 我會去找尋安慰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3\fn華文楷體\fs20\1c&HE0E0E0&}奧利維修{\r}
