Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:23.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Bonnie? - Who is it?\N{\rCHT}- 邦妮？- 誰啊？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:29.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Donovan?\N{\rCHT}唐納文？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:33.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Bonnie? - Yes?\N{\rCHT}- 邦妮？- 什麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:37.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Donovan!\N{\rCHT}唐納文{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:47.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,In here.\N{\rCHT}這裡面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:03:01.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes? Donovan, is everything all right? - Yeah, the production meeting was put off,\N{\rCHT}- 唐納文 沒事吧？- 製片會議取消{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:04.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,- so I thought... Who's here? - Here?\N{\rCHT}- 所以我… 誰在這裡？- 這裡？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:06.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Who owns that piece-of-shit van down there?\N{\rCHT}門外那輛破車是誰的？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:13.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's just a guy going door to door selling pool cleaner.\N{\rCHT}只是泳池篩檢程式的推銷員{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:15.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,So why'd he lock himself in the den?\N{\rCHT}那他怎麼會躲在裡面？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:19.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, he... Oh, God.\N{\rCHT}他… 天啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:22.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,You remember my friend Ollie?\N{\rCHT}記得我朋友奧利嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:25.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ollie Olerud? Short, cretinous wanker.\N{\rCHT}奧利歐勒露？又矮又蠢的傢伙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:29.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Ollie's in there? - Yes.\N{\rCHT}- 奧利在裡面？- 對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:31.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,I see.\N{\rCHT}原來如此{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:35.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad he finally got himself a job.\N{\rCHT}真高興他終於找到工作了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:40.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'd always picked him as some sort of deadbeat, but happy to be proved wrong.\N{\rCHT}還以為他會終生失業 幸虧我看錯了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:44.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,So he's selling pool cleaner now? Well, this is the neighborhood for that.\N{\rCHT}他在推銷泳池篩檢程式？來這區對了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:46.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just door to door, "Running low on chlorine?" That kind of thing.\N{\rCHT}上門推銷"低氯氣"那種？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:51.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's quite a coincidence him dropping by, and you two knowing each other so well.\N{\rCHT}來得真巧 你們還是老相識{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:54.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Donovan, please. Let's just all talk. I mean, I think...\N{\rCHT}唐納文 有事慢慢談 我覺得…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:58.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,How you doing, Donovan? How you doing, man?\N{\rCHT}唐納文 你好嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:00.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good day, Ollie. I'm great. You?\N{\rCHT}奧利 我很好 你呢？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:05.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hey, can't complain, man. - Excellent.\N{\rCHT}- 還可以啦 - 好極了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:08.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, let's get right down to it, then, shall we?\N{\rCHT}廢話少說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:10.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll take a couple of vacuum hoses.\N{\rCHT}我們要買幾條吸水管{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:13.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,We probably need a new filter around about now. Maybe...\N{\rCHT}過濾網可能也要更換 還有…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:16.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, darling. Do we actually have a swimming pool?\N{\rCHT}等一下 我們有游泳池嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:20.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay. Okay, man. Now let's be reasonable about this, okay?\N{\rCHT}大家理智點 好嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:24.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,So you caught me porking... Having relations with your old lady.\N{\rCHT}你發現我和你女人偷情… 有曖昧關係{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:25.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,God.\N{\rCHT}天啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:30.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,And now, we're all feeling just a little bit embarrassed by the whole thing, so...\N{\rCHT}現在大家都有點不好意思 所以…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:36.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,What the hey, man? I mean, I know it's a drag and all, but these things...\N{\rCHT}其實是小事 不用小事化大…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:41.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey, hey. We didn't actually have sex.\N{\rCHT}嘿 我們沒有上床{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:46.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,I was depressed, 'cause I'm impotent, you know.\N{\rCHT}我因為性無能而感到憂鬱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:48.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Unable to achieve an erection.\N{\rCHT}不能勃起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:53.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have been for over a year now, man, and I needed someone to talk to.\N{\rCHT}已經有一年多了 我只想找人傾訴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:56.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean, think about it, man. A year without an erection?\N{\rCHT}一年不能勃起？你說多慘啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:58.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leave him alone!\N{\rCHT}不准碰他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:05.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,You should have seen this coming, you Australian piece of shit!\N{\rCHT}你早就該知道了 死澳洲佬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:09.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bitch. That's my Daytime Television Lifetime Achievement Award.\N{\rCHT}賤人 那是我的電視終生成就獎耶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:11.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cheesy bastard!\N{\rCHT}下流的混蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:15.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,You whore!\N{\rCHT}臭婊子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:19.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Christ!\N{\rCHT}天啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:23.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay!\N{\rCHT}好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:29.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, you want fun and games? All right.\N{\rCHT}好 你想玩？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:34.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll give you fun and games. Explain this away.\N{\rCHT}我就陪你玩玩 看你怎麼解釋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:44.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ollie!\N{\rCHT}奧利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's my Jag! That's my Jag!\N{\rCHT}我的積架呀 我的積架呀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:49.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's my bloody Jag!\N{\rCHT}那是我他媽的積架呀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:54.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,You bitch! Bitch! Bitch!\N{\rCHT}賤貨 賤貨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, baby!\N{\rCHT}再見 寶貝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, what are you looking at?\N{\rCHT}有什麼好看的？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:09.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Explain this away, darling.\N{\rCHT}看你怎麼解釋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3\fn華文楷體\fs20\1c&HE0E0E0&}老婆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3\fn華文楷體\fs20\1c&HE0E0E0&}婚前協議{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:51.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Miles Massey's office. - Hey, it's me. Any messages?\N{\rCHT}- 邁爾斯梅西辦公室 - 是我 有沒有留言？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:54.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah. Quite a few. Where are you? - Just whitening.\N{\rCHT}- 有不少 你在那裡？- 我正在漂牙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:56.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jim says he wants a meeting today if possible.\N{\rCHT}吉姆說要開會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:59.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What else? - Chapman says his wife is now in Tahoe.\N{\rCHT}- 還有呢？- 查普曼說她太太在太浩湖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:01.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, tell Amstedler I'll return in 20 minutes.\N{\rCHT}告訴阿姆斯特德我20分鐘後回去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:05.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get Wrigley to look up Oliphant V. Oliphant, Commonwealth of Virginia,\N{\rCHT}叫雷格利翻查 維吉尼亞州的奧利芬檔案{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:07.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,for its relevance in the Chapman filing.\N{\rCHT}作為查普曼離婚案參考資料{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:09.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oliphant v. Oliphant. ReleVance in Chapman.\N{\rCHT}奧利芬檔案 查普曼離婚案參考資料{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:11.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,She said she took the kids to Tahoe?\N{\rCHT}她帶小孩去太浩湖？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:12.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,- That's right. - Wait. Which side of Tahoe?\N{\rCHT}- 是的 - 太浩湖的哪邊？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:14.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,She said it was a cruise.\N{\rCHT}她說是遊湖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, if the cruise goes all the way around the lake,\N{\rCHT}如果船繞著湖走一圈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:18.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,she's left the state, and she's in breach.\N{\rCHT}就會出本州水域 她就違法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:22.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tell Wrigley to prepare a filing to attach. Mmm-hmm.\N{\rCHT}叫雷格利準備提出訴訟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,Everything.\N{\rCHT}列出全部資產{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:27.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Primary residence, beach house, ski cabin, auto, stocks, bonds, dental floss.\N{\rCHT}住宅 夏日別墅 冬季別墅 車 股票 債券 牙線{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:28.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gonna lose you.\N{\rCHT}要掛斷了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,And tell Fred Armatrading that\N{\rCHT}告訴佛瑞德艾馬崔汀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:33.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,we have pictures of his wife with the oral surgeon.\N{\rCHT}我們拍到他太太和口腔醫生的照片{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:37.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, and get a fruit and pastry basket in the conference room for my 9:30.\N{\rCHT}為會議室準備好 九點半會議的水果麵包{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:38.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Didn't have time for breakfast this morning.\N{\rCHT}今天還沒有時間吃早餐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:42.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Where are you? - Coming at you.\N{\rCHT}- 你在哪裡？- 走向你那邊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:46.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Your 9:00 is here. Bonnie Donaly. - Bonnie Donaly.\N{\rCHT}- 九點的客人來到 邦妮唐諾裡 - 邦妮唐諾裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:55.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Donaly.\N{\rCHT}唐諾裡太太{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:12.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, your husband did show remarkable foresight in taking those pictures.\N{\rCHT}你丈夫拍下這幾幅照片 確實有遠見{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:15.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,And, yes, absent a swimming pool,\N{\rCHT}沒有泳池{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:18.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,the presence of a pool man would appear to be suspicious.\N{\rCHT}卻有泳池人員 難免令人起疑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:23.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,But, madam, who is the real victim here? Let me suggest to you the following.\N{\rCHT}不過 真正的受害人是誰？讓我向你建議{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:27.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your husband, who on a prior occasion had slapped you, beat you.\N{\rCHT}你丈夫曾經摑你 打你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:29.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I think that word is not inappropriate. - No, I...\N{\rCHT}- 用詞相信不恰當 - 不 我…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:33.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let me finish, please. I'm not concerned with who slapped whom first.\N{\rCHT}讓我說完 我不管誰先動手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your husband, who had beaten you repeatedly...\N{\rCHT}你丈夫不斷打你…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:36.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, he never...\N{\rCHT}不 他沒有…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:39.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Please. Repeatedly, was at the time, brandishing your firearm.\N{\rCHT}不斷打 還揮動你的手槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:42.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,- It was his gun. - And we'll get it back for you.\N{\rCHT}- 他的手槍 - 我們會替你取回手槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:47.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Trying, in his rage, to shoot an acquaintance, a friend of long standing.\N{\rCHT}蓄意槍擊一位老朋友{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:48.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,They never really cared for each other.\N{\rCHT}他們合不來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:51.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,And if not for your cool-headed intervention,\N{\rCHT}若不是你冷靜 及時制止{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:54.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,his tantrum might have ended this schmo's life and ruined his own.\N{\rCHT}他早已殺害無辜 自毀前途{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:59.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,As for the sexual indiscretion which he imagined took place,\N{\rCHT}所謂越軌行為 是他無中生有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:03.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,wasn't it, in fact, he who was sleeping with the pool man?\N{\rCHT}其實是他自己搭上泳池人員？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:10.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,No? Am I going too far here? Were his sexual... No.\N{\rCHT}不對？我的假設太大膽了？他不是那種… 不{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:12.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I don't... - Sorry. I'm not omniscient.\N{\rCHT}- 我不… - 抱歉 我不是先知{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:16.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,The point is that he acted upon an assumption which he cannot prove,\N{\rCHT}重點是他無法證明他的假設{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:19.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,and, I take it, you deny.\N{\rCHT}而你又否認{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:20.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Well... - Fine. I'll take the case.\N{\rCHT}- 這… - 好 我接辦本案{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:24.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's imperative that I meet with Oliver Olerud before we proceed any further,\N{\rCHT}我必須先和奧利歐勒露談談{\r}
